    "maintainer_can_modify": true,
    "title": "dbwrapper: avoid copying unobfuscated iterator values",
    "user": {
      "login": "CruzMolina",
      "id": 7537712,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjc1Mzc3MTI=",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7537712?v=4",
      "gravatar_id": "",
      "url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina",
      "html_url": "https://github.com/CruzMolina",
      "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/followers",
      "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/following%7B/other_user%7D",
      "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/gists%7B/gist_id%7D",
      "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/starred%7B/owner%7D%7B/repo%7D",
      "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/subscriptions",
      "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/orgs",
      "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/repos",
      "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/events%7B/privacy%7D",
      "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CruzMolina/received_events",
      "type": "User",
      "site_admin": false,
      "name": null,
      "patch_url": null
    },
    "body": "### Motivation\n\n`CDBIterator::GetValue()` currently copies the current LevelDB value into a\ntemporary `DataStream` before deserializing it. This is only needed when\ndatabase obfuscation is enabled, because deobfuscation mutates the value bytes\nbefore they are read.\n\n### Change\n\nUse `SpanReader` to deserialize iterator values directly when the database has\nno obfuscation key. Keep the existing `DataStream` path for obfuscated\ndatabases.\n\nThis mirrors the existing `GetKey()` borrowed-span path while preserving the\nold exception-to-`false` behavior.\n\n### Test\n\n```bash\ncmake --build build --target test_bitcoin\nbuild/bin/test_bitcoin --run_test=dbwrapper_tests\n```",
